<h3 class="mbs-4">Mixing font families</h3>
<p>
  We can mix different fonts for different scripts. Here's
  Tahoma used for Arabic and Verdana used for English.
</p>
<div class="demo-container">
  <p class="font-tahoma" dir="rtl">
    نص حكيم له سر قاطع وذو شأن عظيم مكتوب على ثوب أخضر ومغلف
    بجلد أزرق
  </p>
  <p class="font-verdana">
    The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.
  </p>
</div>

<p>
  Mixing fonts can cause iconsistencies; look at the
  variance in stroke weight and line height between Arabic
  in the Tahomo font and English in Impact.
</p>

<div class="demo-container">
